{"tid":2241470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍灣 facial","createTime":"2020-10-13T10:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T10:40:15.000Z","uid":348982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29fe91886bfe59286be03932c945c8a860e643eb","tid":2241470,"uid":348982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"九龍灣 美容 晴x粧<br />\n<br />\n淘大店搬到呢家既德寶店<br />\n1) 人手嚴重萎縮，間舖只有2個負責人做埋美容師。九成時間得一個人，負責聽電話，落booking，接客，同時間接2個客。次次做緊清黑頭，美容師都會走開聽電話/接客。<br />\n<br />\n2) 本身係買左plan ，但疫情停業加搬舖停業。 無補番plan時間，我個plan 過埋期，逼你再買新plan先可以extend 番<br />\n<br />\n3) booking 成日無位。人手太少，打電話去booking，話無位，叫下星期再打去，結果下星期都係無位。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好中伏"},{"pid":"b2193eb0afbc6beb67c95bad0b2c9afed46217c5","tid":2241470,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"男人老狗做咩facial"},{"pid":"c62902054b83a77a4f440213ba86a0eb15c7cd22","tid":2241470,"uid":348982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2193eb0afbc6beb67c95bad0b2c9afed46217c5","tid":2241470,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"男人老狗做咩facial"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"可能我係女人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16015e6db9ab74320194c0e919898bdae6eb80d","tid":2241470,"uid":77901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"係打就打全名啦x你老母咩"}]}